# Copy to .env only if you need to override the data source.
#
# By default the site reads from its own serverless function at /api/data,
# which fetches StrengthLevel server-side. You normally do NOT need to set
# anything here. When the site is opened as a bare local file (no server),
# it automatically falls back to the bundled sample data.

# Override the data endpoint (rarely needed):
# VITE_DATA_URL=/api/data
